# Insight distillation deny list
# 1 line per pattern. Lines starting with '#' are comments.
#
# Syntax:
#   path:<glob>      Skip jsonl files whose absolute path matches the glob (** allowed).
#                    Applied at the file enumeration stage, before parsing.
#   text:<regex>     Drop individual insight bodies whose text matches this regex.
#                    Applied per-insight after extraction.
#
# Examples:
#   path:**/projects/-home-myname-secret-project/**
#   path:**/work-confidential/**
#   text:internal-corp-id-\d+
#
# This file is created once by chezmoi and is never overwritten by subsequent
# applies. Edit freely.
